description: Nestled in the vibrant heart of Parramatta CBD, mere meters from the tranquil river, this exquisite 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom apartment offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and urban convenience.

As you step inside, you're greeted by a spacious and inviting atmosphere, highlighted by a generously sized covered balcony offering a peaceful retreat amidst the bustling cityscape. The apartment boasts a thoughtfully designed layout, featuring a well-appointed kitchen with ample storage and preparation space. The combined living and dining area seamlessly flow together, providing a versatile space for relaxation and entertainment.

Both bedrooms have built in wardrobes with the master also having an ensuite, allowing you to retreat into your sanctuary after a big day enjoying all Parramatta has to offer. Positioned minutes away from cafes, schools, dining and nightlife. Experience the ease of city life with close proximity to the train station, ferry wharf and the new light rail just down the end of the street!
• 2 bedrooms both with built in wardrobes
• Main bathroom with a bath and ensuite off master bedroom
Please contact James on 0416 910 340 or Frankie on 0450 680 808 with any questions or for a private inspection.
